    <briefdescription>
<para>The native base class for the content widget representing a setting category. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The native base class for the content widget representing a setting category.</para>
<para>This is the superclass of <ref refid="classUSFCategoryTab__Branch" kindref="compound">USFCategoryTab_Branch</ref>, which displays a branch-type category with subcategories, and <ref refid="classUSFCategoryTab__Leaf" kindref="compound">USFCategoryTab_Leaf</ref>, which displays a leaf-type category with setting entries. <simplesect kind="note"><para><computeroutput>Abstract</computeroutput> <computeroutput>BlueprintType</computeroutput> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
